CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 20, 1938, p.13 reads: "Peabody Stalwarts - Three reasons why Peabody High School is currently leading Section 1 of the city cage race are shown above. Left to right are John Wideman,  Max Holm, and Carl Kohlman.  All three are seniors. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Peabody High School basketball players John Wideman, Max Holm, and Carl Kohlman, wearing 1758 Pittsburgh Bicentennial 1958-59 patch on shorts
